<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Maximus Vickers Founder & Entrepreneur</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  :root {
    --cream: #0A0A0A; --off-white: #111111; --ink: #F0EDE8;
    --mid: #A09A94; --light: #5C5752; --accent: #7B2FBE; --rule: #222222;
  }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif; background: var(--cream); color: var(--ink); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; overflow-x: hidden; }
  nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1.2rem 5vw; background: rgba(10,10,10,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .nav-logo { font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.03em; color: var(--ink); text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .nav-logo img { width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 6px; object-fit: contain; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { font-size: 0.74rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--mid); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  section { padding: 7rem 5vw; }
  .section-header { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
  .section-num { font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--light); }
  .section-title { font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 300; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  #home { min-height: 100vh; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: center; padding: 0 5vw; padding-top: 5rem; gap: 4rem; }
  .hero-eyebrow { font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .hero-eyebrow::before { content: ""; display: inline-block; width: 36px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent); }
  .hero-name { font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif; font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 6vw, 5.5rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
  .hero-name em { font-style: italic; color: var(--mid); }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--mid); font-weight: 300; max-width: 420px; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .btn-primary { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.76rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500; padding: 0.9rem 2rem; transition: background 0.25s, gap 0.25s; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent); gap: 1.2rem; }
  .btn-primary svg, .btn-outline svg { transition: transform 0.25s; }
  .btn-primary:hover svg { transform: translateX(4px); }
  .btn-outline { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; border: 1px solid var(--ink); color: var(--ink); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.74rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500; padding: 0.85rem 1.8rem; transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s; }
  .btn-outline:hover { background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); }
  .photo-frame { width: 100%; max-width: 400px; aspect-ratio: 3/4; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .photo-frame img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center top; }
  .photo-label { font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--light); text-align: right; }
  .hero-visual { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1.5rem; }
  #about { background: var(--off-white); }
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr; gap: 6rem; align-items: start; }
  .about-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--mid); border: 1px solid var(--rule); padding: 0.4rem 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-right: 0.4rem; }
  .about-tags { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .about-body p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--mid); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
  .about-body p strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }
  .edu-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
  .edu-card { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem; border: 1px solid var(--rule); background: #161616; }
  .edu-card img { width: 44px; height: 44px; object-fit: contain; flex-shrink: 0; border-radius: 6px; }
  .edu-card-degree { font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }
  .edu-card-meta { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }
  .edu-card-year { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--light); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .badge { font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem; border: 1px solid var(--accent); color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; display: inline-block; margin: 0.15rem 0.15rem 0 0; }
  .resume-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.8fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: start; }
  .resume-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .resume-section-title { font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; font-weight: 500; }
  .skill-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 0.6rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--mid); }
  .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--rule); }
  .dot.filled { background: var(--accent); }
  .skill-dots { display: flex; gap: 5px; }
  .experience-item { padding-bottom: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .experience-item:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
  .exp-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .exp-title { font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); }
  .exp-date { font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--light); }
  .exp-company { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .exp-company img { width: 20px; height: 20px; object-fit: contain; border-radius: 4px; }
  .exp-bullets { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.55rem; }
  .exp-bullets li { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--mid); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.65; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; }
  .exp-bullets li::before { content: "·"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--accent); font-size: 0.9rem; }
  #portfolio { background: var(--off-white); }
  .portfolio-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .portfolio-card { background: #161616; border: 1px solid var(--rule); overflow: hidden; transition: transform 0.25s; }
  .portfolio-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .portfolio-card-visual { height: 160px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden; }
  .portfolio-card-body { padding: 1.4rem; }
  .portfolio-card-tag { font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .portfolio-card-title { font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .portfolio-card-desc { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--mid); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.65; }
  .blog-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .blog-card { border: 1px solid var(--rule); background: #161616; overflow: hidden; cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.2s; }
  .blog-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); }
  .blog-card-header { height: 140px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .blog-card-body { padding: 1.4rem; }
  .blog-tag { font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .blog-title { font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.3; }
  .blog-excerpt { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--mid); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .blog-read-more { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }
  .modal-overlay { display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(26,23,20,0.7); z-index: 200; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 2rem; }
  .modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }
  .modal { background: #111111; max-width: 700px; width: 100%; max-height: 85vh; overflow-y: auto; padding: 3rem; position: relative; }
  .modal-close { position: absolute; top: 1.5rem; right: 1.5rem; background: none; border: none; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--mid); cursor: pointer; }
  .modal-tag { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .modal-title { font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.2; }
  .modal-body p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--mid); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  #video { background: var(--off-white); }
  .video-placeholder { border: 2px dashed var(--rule); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem; height: 400px; background: #161616; max-width: 720px; }
  .video-placeholder p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--light); text-align: center; line-height: 1.6; }
  #contact { background: #111111; }
  #contact .section-title { color: var(--ink); }
  #contact .section-num { color: var(--light); }
  .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6rem; align-items: start; }
  .contact-intro { font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .contact-intro em { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; }
  .contact-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem; padding: 1.5rem 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .contact-label { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--mid); }
  .contact-value { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--mid); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; font-weight: 300; }
  .contact-value:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .linkedin-cta { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; background: var(--accent); color: var(--ink); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500; padding: 1rem 2rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
  .linkedin-cta:hover { opacity: 0.88; }
  footer { padding: 2rem 5vw; background: #000000; border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }
  footer span { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--mid); letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  footer a { color: var(--mid); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.72rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  .hero-eyebrow { animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards; }
  .hero-name    { animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.12s ease both; }
  .hero-sub     { animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.22s ease both; }
  .btn-primary  { animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.32s ease both; }
  .photo-frame  { animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.1s ease both; }
  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    #home { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding-top: 7rem; }
    .hero-visual { align-items: center; }
    .photo-frame { max-width: 280px; }
    .about-grid, .resume-layout, .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .portfolio-grid, .blog-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .edu-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .nav-links { gap: 1.4rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .portfolio-grid, .blog-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a class="nav-logo" href="#home">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="FourMeasure" />
    Maximus Vickers
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#resume">Resume</a></li>
    <li><a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
    <li><a href="#blog">Blog</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="home">
  <div>
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Student Entrepreneur</div>
    <h1 class="hero-name">Maximus<br><em>Vickers.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Founder &amp; CEO building a scalable consumer tech platform for music discovery. Senior at the University of Miami Herbert Business School.</p>
    <a class="btn-primary" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/maximus-vickers-bb69672b1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      Connect on LinkedIn
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M1 7h12M7 1l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-visual">
    <div class="photo-frame"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Maximus Vickers" /></div>
    <span class="photo-label">Maximus Vickers · Miami, FL</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="section-header"><span class="section-num">01</span><h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2></div>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="about-tags">
        <span class="about-tag">Entrepreneurship</span>
        <span class="about-tag">Brand Strategy</span>
        <span class="about-tag">Music Tech</span>
        <span class="about-tag">Management</span>
        <span class="about-tag">Bilingual</span>
      </div>
    </div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;margin-top:0.5rem;">
        <span style="font-size:1.8rem;" title="Canada">🇨🇦</span>
        <span style="font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--light);">Calgary, AB</span>
        <span style="color:var(--rule);font-size:0.8rem;">→</span>
        <span style="font-size:1.8rem;" title="United States">🇺🇸</span>
        <span style="font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--light);">Miami, FL</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-body">
      <p>Founder &amp; CEO of FourMeasure, a self-funded social platform redefining how people rate, review, and discover music. I led the company end-to-end across product, brand, and technical development, building an early user base through direct outreach and interviews. FourMeasure helps emerging artists gain discovery while adding a social layer to everyday listeners' music identity.</p>
      <p>I'm a senior at the University of Miami Herbert Business School pursuing a B.B.A. in Management with a minor in Entrepreneurship. I operate comfortably in diverse environments and actively seek new industries and challenges that expand my perspective. I approach business with intensity and ownership, holding myself to a high standard of execution, efficiency, and continuous growth.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- RESUME -->
<section id="resume">
  <div class="section-header"><span class="section-num">02</span><h2 class="section-title">Resume</h2></div>
  <div class="edu-cards">
    <div class="edu-card">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="University of Miami" />
      <div>
        <div class="edu-card-degree">University of Miami</div>
        <div class="edu-card-meta">B.B.A. Management · Entrepreneurship Minor</div>
        <div class="edu-card-year">2023 2026 · Coral Gables, FL</div>
        <span class="badge">Presidential Scholar</span>
        <span class="badge">Provost's Honor Roll</span>
        <span class="badge">NSLS</span>
        <span class="badge">Economics Club</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="edu-card">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Miami Dade College" />
      <div>
        <div class="edu-card-degree">Miami Dade College</div>
        <div class="edu-card-meta">A.A. Business Administration</div>
        <div class="edu-card-year">Oct 2022 Jul 2023 · Miami, FL</div>
        <span class="badge">GPA 4.0</span>
        <span class="badge">Dean's List</span>
        <span class="badge">Pi Kappa Phi</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="resume-layout">
    <div>
      <div class="resume-section">
        <div class="resume-section-title">Skills</div>
        <div class="skill-row">GTM Strategy <span class="skill-dots"><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span></span></div>
        <div class="skill-row">Brand Repositioning <span class="skill-dots"><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot"></span></span></div>
        <div class="skill-row">Product Roadmapping <span class="skill-dots"><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot"></span></span></div>
        <div class="skill-row">Financial Modeling <span class="skill-dots"><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span></span></div>
        <div class="skill-row">Data Analysis <span class="skill-dots"><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot filled"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span></span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-section">
        <div class="resume-section-title">Languages</div>
        <div class="skill-row">English <span style="font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--light);">Native</span></div>
        <div class="skill-row">French <span style="font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--light);">Fluent</span></div>
        <div class="skill-row">Spanish <span style="font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--light);">Conversational</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-section">
        <div class="resume-section-title">Contact</div>
        <div class="skill-row" style="border:none;padding:0.3rem 0;font-size:0.83rem;">Miami, FL</div>
        <div class="skill-row" style="border:none;padding:0.3rem 0;font-size:0.83rem;"><a href="tel:7868482408" style="color:var(--mid);text-decoration:none;">(786) 848-2408</a></div>
        <div class="skill-row" style="border:none;padding:0.3rem 0;font-size:0.83rem;"><a href="mailto:mdv87@miami.edu" style="color:var(--mid);text-decoration:none;">mdv87@miami.edu</a></div>
        <div class="skill-row" style="border:none;padding:0.3rem 0;font-size:0.83rem;"><a href="mailto:maximus@fourmeasure.com" style="color:var(--mid);text-decoration:none;">maximus@fourmeasure.com</a></div>
        <div class="skill-row" style="border:none;padding:0.3rem 0;font-size:0.83rem;"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/maximus-vickers-bb69672b1" target="_blank" style="color:var(--mid);text-decoration:none;">LinkedIn</a></div>
      </div>
      <a class="btn-outline" href="data:application/pdf;base64," download="Maximus_Vickers_Resume.pdf" style="margin-top:1rem;">
        Download Resume (PDF)
        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 13 13" fill="none"><path d="M6.5 1v8M2 9l4.5 3L11 9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="experience-item">
        <div class="exp-header"><span class="exp-title">Founder &amp; CEO</span><span class="exp-date">Nov 2024 Present</span></div>
        <div class="exp-company"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="FourMeasure" /> FourMeasure Corp · Full-time</div>
        <ul class="exp-bullets">
          <li>Built MVP and lead product roadmap, UX direction, and beta launch strategy for a consumer social platform focused on music discovery.</li>
          <li>Contracted and manage a cross-functional team of engineers and designers; invested $50,000+ in founder capital to fund product development and infrastructure.</li>
          <li>Grew pre-launch waitlist to 100+ users through organic community-building and targeted social outreach.</li>
          <li>Conducted 75+ user interviews to validate engagement loop and refine feature set based on retention signals and qualitative feedback.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="experience-item">
        <div class="exp-header"><span class="exp-title">Innovation Strategist</span><span class="exp-date">May 2025 Sep 2025</span></div>
        <div class="exp-company"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="US Flood Control" /> Tiger Dams · Innovation Strategist</div>
        <ul class="exp-bullets">
          <li>Spearheaded full website redesign and repositioning of Tiger Dams from a B2B-only brand to a dual consumer–commercial platform, unlocking an untapped residential market segment.</li>
          <li>Rebuilt site architecture and streamlined purchasing flow to make product selection and checkout more efficient for everyday consumers.</li>
          <li>Collaborated with company leadership to shape pricing, refine messaging, and develop go-to-market strategy for the new consumer product line.</li>
        </ul>
